1622860,"uid":138092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:56:56.000Z","msg":"最有用就係遍地開花，街坊熟悉地形能近能退，反而好多狗未必住呢區冇咁好應變，住開嘅又驚比街坊知。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋布陣佈防部署需時長，玩對峙就最啱佢哋，下下拉玩圍捕拉撚曬你地。橫掂依家再打再殺平民都已經冇事。但係區區開花，佢哋人手唔夠最多就係搭車黎黎去去，去到人又散曬搞唔撚掂。<br />\n<br />\n同埋區區開花對唔係好多錢嘅人來講係最好嘅方法，唔使擔心冇錢搭車冇錢食飯。"},{"pid":"2a59e546988b9909c2959e7527cc404984692c86","tid":1622860,"uid":50284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"但無可否認，大家識得反擊的確係可以增加士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f585a5671a99a9e18a294861003c25feb857b56b","tid":1622860,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c1616e400d2a00d6be8b47d06130b861dfd69aa5","tid":1622860,"uid":224479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"998b51757f6853d865ae4729805d0bc13042b143","tid":1622860,"uid":50284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be4bcef9764ec708b833a5aec6d7d1ad0bffb378","tid":1622860,"uid":224479,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d891c00829cdd1f39b2b5adacd359483534018","tid":1622860,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:59:05.000Z","msg":"唔好輕敵"},{"pid":"3bd50d428dbdf9b90597b9af2d064c3c48e78448","tid":1622860,"uid":306999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:59:27.000Z","msg":"孫臏減灶？等人哋冇乜戒心先出嚟咬"},{"pid":"0134079365f2d33a7bc9a71cb2eca04f2e0b6623","tid":1622860,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f872